{"tid":1366494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗吃喝玩樂介紹","createTime":"2019-07-26T03:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T03:40:42.000Z","uid":85451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7904675d230a3dbb7fdc4e52858edf432ef337","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"yoho<br />\n都多野買 又a&amp;e JW h&amp;m GW 買衫<br />\n食野又多choice<br />\n又可以睇戲<br />\n<br />\n唔舒服記得去博愛醫院喇<br />\n<br />\n大馬路兩邊都可港式野食 不過有啲係鄉黑經營<br />\n又可以去運動舖買下行山用品<br />\n<br />\n雞地個邊又有籃球場 體育館 <br />\n可以全民運動<br />\n<br />\n屏山又有大球場<br />\n<br />\n過黎元朗都多方法<br />\n紅van 上水車 旺角車<br />\n<br />\n巴士<br />\n269D 沙田<br />\n268A 268C 觀塘<br />\n269B 紅磡<br />\n<br />\n大欖可以轉279 去粉嶺 265m 去荃灣<br />\n有咩車上左先又可以大欖隧道轉車<br />\n<br />\n仲可以入68 or 68F 入parkyoho 睇樓<br />\n268m再由parkyoho去荃灣<br />\n<br />\n輕鐵是但上一架去左屯門or天水圍又可以轉車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎forward 或者modify"},{"pid":"d289102b63af0deea3e06a4b90a6184d9d311602","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b150c97bf7c62a09265fefd469e6b0716311fa","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"copy and paste"},{"pid":"e2b0437bfba03abca26a10e5dad609b04027804f","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:35:59.000Z","msg":"1212"},{"pid":"651e426e53d9c98b08f22ceb070330408e4e2463","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"去YL 打邊邊爐 放題先"},{"pid":"9cf83953159f4ec13667ce4c97648bc9abccfff8","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"食壽司"},{"pid":"fcba4eb71e059f999ba1dd7d7a87e3cd024c18c4","tid":1366494,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:37:10.000Z",